content: I'm planning a trip to visit my family soon and I need some help with gift ideas for my cousin John, who just graduated from college with a degree in engineering today. I was thinking of getting him something personalized, like an engraved accessory or a customized item for his new job. Do you have any suggestions? By the way, I just got back from my friend Rachel's master's degree graduation ceremony yesterday, which was amazing - she must be thrilled to finally have that behind her.
